You are not a ruiner.

39:53.959 --> 39:55.794
Okay, do you hear me?

39:55.827 --> 39:57.863
You are the opposite.
You're a-a put-together-er.

39:57.896 --> 39:59.865
Paula, you don't know
what you're talking about,

39:59.898 --> 40:01.032
and it doesn't even make sense.

40:01.066 --> 40:03.769
Oh, okay, you want to know
what you put together-ered?

40:03.802 --> 40:05.804
My marriage.

40:05.837 --> 40:07.739
What?
Yes!

40:07.773 --> 40:10.776
I mean, who knew a little
vandalism would be, like,

40:10.809 --> 40:14.212
the most amazing
foreplay we had ever had?!

40:14.245 --> 40:16.848
I mean, look at
this text from Scott.

40:16.882 --> 40:18.517
I mean, look at
all these emojis.

40:18.550 --> 40:20.519
He sent me, like,
a unicorn and a panda.

40:20.552 --> 40:22.821
Hmm.
And, like, 11 different
kinds of hearts.

40:22.854 --> 40:24.723
Oh.
(laughing)

40:24.756 --> 40:26.658
Oh, no, no, don't
scroll there. Oh.
Whoa.

40:26.692 --> 40:27.826
Yeah. Okay.
Wow.

40:27.859 --> 40:29.528
Sorry. I'm sorry
you had to see that.

40:29.561 --> 40:33.198
No. You... you go.

40:33.231 --> 40:35.601
Okay, but listen to me.

40:35.634 --> 40:37.836
You and Josh--
you're on a journey.

40:37.869 --> 40:39.805
Okay? So there's
gonna be peaks,

40:39.838 --> 40:41.640
but there's also
gonna be valleys.

40:41.673 --> 40:45.511
And yes, maybe even a
long, dry, flat plateau

40:45.544 --> 40:47.045
called "my-kids-are-little,
don't-touch-me."

40:47.078 --> 40:51.617
But the valleys are gonna
make those peaks even sweeter.

40:51.650 --> 40:54.853
So... take a deep breath.

40:58.857 --> 41:01.860
Look how beautiful
it is today.

41:01.893 --> 41:06.632
And know that everything
is gonna be okay.

41:06.665 --> 41:10.936
And if it's not,
we will make it okay.

41:10.969 --> 41:13.705
I promise you.

41:15.273 --> 41:17.242
Are you sure?

41:17.275 --> 41:19.845
We will find a way.

41:19.878 --> 41:21.780
Come here.

41:21.813 --> 41:23.915
I swear.

41:25.951 --> 41:28.253
I think I have a UTI.

41:32.591 --> 41:34.793
Harry, did you okay
a police escort to get a woman

41:34.826 --> 41:36.094
to her ex-boyfriend's
house faster?

41:36.127 --> 41:37.996
Yes, sir, but you have
to understand...

41:38.029 --> 41:40.566
Judge Spenser, that was
an unnecessary expenditure,

41:40.599 --> 41:42.934
not to mention
you put our citizens at risk.

41:42.968 --> 41:44.636
But sir, it was urgent.

41:44.670 --> 41:46.137
It was a text-mergency.

41:46.171 --> 41:48.306
You mean a text-tastrophe?

41:48.339 --> 41:50.976
Is that what caught on?

41:51.009 --> 41:52.310
It figures.

41:52.343 --> 41:53.679
Damn it!

41:53.712 --> 41:54.846
Judge Spenser,

41:54.880 --> 41:56.882
why are you getting so upset?

41:57.916 --> 41:59.885
What's this really about?

41:59.918 --> 42:03.254
I left my wife for a prostitute.
(crying)

